    <item>
      <title>对特朗普的担忧导致新兴市场股市遭遇 1 月以来最糟糕的一个月</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-24/fear-of-trump-sends-em-stocks-toward-worst-month-since-january</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于美国总统大选前的紧张情绪和中国刺激计划的失望导致投资者远离风险较高的资产，新兴市场股市遭遇了美联储上个月降息以来最长的连跌周期。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-24/fear-of-trump-sends-em-stocks-toward-worst-month-since-january</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 24 Oct 2024 11:08:23 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
